Meru Teaching and Referral Hospital has unveiled an ambitious plan which will see it transform into a specialised health care facility — Level Six — in the next five years.
The hospital projects that it will require about Sh21 billion over the period and intends to spend Sh1 billion in procurement of specialised medical equipment.



